scripts.clean: rm -rf yarn.lock && rm -rf package-lock.json && yarn cache clean && rm -rf node_modules && watchman watch-del-all && yarn && rm -frv $TMPDIR/react-* | echo $(wc -l) 'react-* Files Removed' && rm -rf $TMPDIR/haste-map-* | echo $(wc -l) 'haste-map-* Files Removed' && rm -rf $TMPDIR/react-native-packager-cache-* | echo $(wc -l) 'react-native-packager-cache-* Files Removed' && rm -rf $TMPDIR/metro-bundler-cache-* | echo $(wc -l) 'metro-bundler-cache-* Files Removed' && rm -rf $TMPDIR/metro-cache-* | echo $(wc -l) 'metro-cache-* Files Removed'
